00:38:58,210 --> 00:39:00,100
we really shouldn't
use this anymore.

904
00:39:00,100 --> 00:39:03,100
But in both of these
cases, sha-1 and MD5,

905
00:39:03,100 --> 00:39:05,620
there's no feasible
preimage attack.

